rComments: Most awesome, kind, knowledgeable prof ever!

She is our private applied teacher. She has good technique but teaches all her students in very different manners. She is very very kind, but sometimes odd. She is kind of funny sometimes, and has excellent intuition. Her private classes are always... INTERESTING...

Nice prof who is very kind to her students. The grading is fair, especially considering the assigned pieces are much harder than what we work on in class. This course starts out slowly and the first playing assignment is a shock as a result. However, later in the course, more time is spent in class preparing assigned pieces and this is helpful.
